high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter and then all the way right to the microwave.
Take the mug out of the microwave.
Step right and face the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge to the left of the wine. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the mug out.
Step left to face the microwave again.
Place the mug back in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a microwave.

high_descs: walk forwards and then hang a right towards the microwave
grab the cup out of the microwave
move to the right a bit and face the fridge
place the cup inside the fridge to cool, then take it back out
move to the left a bit and face the microwave again
place the cup inside of the microwave and close the door
anns.task_desc: place a cooled cup inside of the microwave

high_descs: Go straight toward the stove, then turn right and go to the counter with the microwave.
Remove the cup from the microwave.
Turn right, then turn left at the fridge.
Chill the cup in the fridge.
Turn left, then right to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the center of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup in the microwave.
